<! [CDATA[
 Donaldson Company Logo
Donaldson Company, Inc. is a vertically integrated filtration company engaged in the production and marketing of air filters used in a variety of industry sectors, including commercial/industrial, aerospace, chemical, alternative energy and pharmaceuticals. Also the company’s research division, located in Minneapolis, Minn., participated in defense-related projects for various military applications. As a multinational company it operates in Belgium, Mexico, China, UK, Thailand, USA, Russia, Japan, Italy, Germany and France. In fiscal year 2016 20.
